reviewText: I don't know who enjoys the episodes more - me or my now 11month old grandson! I plan on probably having all the episodes - I already own 10 DVDs! The cartoons are so refreshing and quite funny too!
Title: Backyardigans: We Arrrr Pirates

reviewText: My children love this DVD in addition to the other Backyardigans DVDs we own. The fact that it contains an episode we'd never seen anywhere else is the icing on the cake. I recommend Backyardigans to anyone who wants to expose their youngsters to different styles of cultural music and dance while stimulating their imaginations.
Title: Backyardigans: We Arrrr Pirates

reviewText: All of my grandchildren LOVE the Backyardigans - and I must say I enjoy them myself!  I have purchased MANY of the Backyardigans DVDs and other related products from Amazon.  Usually Amazon has the best price but I have found some things lower priced at other vendors.  I have never found a better selection than what Amazon offers though.  I just wish they would give a better description for some of their items that come with multiple episodes.
